officialTitle: Tramadol Versus Celecoxib in Reducing Pain Associated With IUD Insertion: A Double Blind Placebo Controlled Trial
inclusionCriteria:
* Women with expected difficult IUD insertion like nulliparous women and women with previous cesarean section.
* Must be FEMALE
* Must have minimum age of 20 Years
* Must have maximum age of 45 Years
exclusionCriteria:
* Previous vaginal delivery.
* Submucous myoma.
* Uterine anomalies.
* Undiagnosed vaginal bleeding.
* Pelvic inflammatory disease.
